PULMONARY
CANDIDIASIS
IN
CYSTIC
FIBROSIS
A
CHILD
WITH
CYSTIC
FIBROSIS
AND
ASTHMA
DEVELOPED
PULMONARY
CANDIDIASIS
PREDISPOSING
FACTORS
IN
THIS
PATIENT
WERE
PROLONGED
ANTIBIOTIC
THERAPY
HIGHDOSE
CORTICOSTEROIDS
AND
INTRAVENOUS
CATHERISATION
A
